Text: Can connect to seeds - check. Reasonable speeds - check. No RARs - check. No bullshit - check. Nice work, Ferrelas. +1.
No folders, no rars, great. Why are there still . instead of spaces? Why is the IMMERSE tag still in the file name? If you're going to neuter torrrents, at least go all they way, not half arsed!
